title: 이달의소녀탐구 #386 (LOONA TV #386)
summary:
0:01 -- HeeJin is explaining HyunJin something about clicking pictures "We have to take pictures of each other."
HyunJin: "Why?"; HeeJin (with a funny face): "Cause the told me do that"; HyunJin: "Umm~"
0:13 -- 2Jin take an official picture with a smartphone as Kim Lip takes an official picture with a DSLR.
0:35 -- "Kim Lip captures the PD camera as well." JinSoul: "Do it like a real photographer."
0:43 -- Lippie starts talking about her hair how it looks luxorious. "It is the color of an eclipse"
Meanwhile HyunJin pops up in the back. Lip: "I think she wants my hair!" and tries it on.
0:55 -- HyunJin: "I think it looks good. Give it to me!?"
